        	<h1>What is Social Media Action Center?</h1>
            <h2>SMAC essentially is a social media-monitoring tool, but with substantially more to help you measure the pulse of your campaign or listening exercise.</h2> 
            <p>SMAC has many unique features not the least being its ability to extract the sentiment values from conversations. Meaning we are able to determine the favorable and unfavorable content directly from the consumer.</p>
<p>With SMAC you now you know the who, what and where of social media. How was the campaign perceived by the audience, what worked and what didn’t. What insights can I take from this and apply to the next program for greater successful.</p>
<p>SMAC is designed to answer all these questions and more. It’s designed to shift the power balance back towards the brand, to give you greater control and a better understanding of consumer dynamics.</p>
